I always loved these two suspenseful movies and this is a nice package fro the price. Super 8 isn't just a kids movie. It's moving and extremely well scripted, acted, and the animation is great. Eagle Eye is also well scripted and acted and has a plot that keeps you guessing...at least for a while.
